<br>
Here are some of my thoughts to add on here.<br>
<br>
You should not be grouping as a warrior/paladin/ShadowKnight/monk/ranger until level 10 at least. There is no real benefit to doing so when you can and will get better xp and skill increases by doing so.<br>
<br>
Get the names of clerics/shaman/druids onto your friends list! You will need them in the level 10+ game.<br>
<br>
Stats and such, they are a lie. As a shaman and a warrior, they do improve performance but not so drastically that they should be sought after over such things as haste and healing.<br>
<br>
Get yourself into the best armor you can and the best weaponry you can. Armor first, weapons second. At level 15, on our server you should be into a full set of bronze at least. If not, give me a tell in game sometime, I have a full set or two of Black Alloy sitting in my bank.<br>
<br>
