<br>
Keep your bandage skill maxed out. After level 24 when your shaman starts doing his Cannibalize Dance for mana, bandage him so he can dance for more mana !<br>
<br>
Killing lots of blues is more efficient xp wise than killing a single even or yellow con mob. At least as a warrior it is.<br>
<br>
Find places where there are TONS of single or double pull mobs and VERY few people to compete with. On this line of thinking, here are my Xp and such for zones (speaking as a barbarian) :<br>
<br>
Level 1-15 Everfrost/BlackBurrow is an awesome area.<br>
6-20 Aviak Guards in Rathe Lake/Beholders Maze<br>
